# Conventional Commits for OmniBrief
#
# <type>: <short description>
#
# Types:
#   fix:     Bug fix
#   feat:    New feature
#   chore:   Maintenance, config, deps
#   refactor: Code change with no functional change
#   docs:    Documentation only
#   perf:    Performance improvement
#   test:    Adding or fixing tests
#   style:   Formatting, missing semicolons, etc.
#
# Examples:
#   fix: handle dns transient failure in ssrf check
#   feat: add url normalization to dedup
#   chore: add pyproject.toml for pip install -e . support
#
